BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-06-02T07:26:10&endDate=2026-06-02T10:38:41">Disruption map.</a>\n\nMetropolitan Line: No service between Baker Street and Aldgate and MINOR DELAYS on the rest of the line due to strike action. Services are operating between Harrow-on-the-Hill and Amersham / Chesham every 30 minutes\, between Harrow-on-the-Hill and Uxbridge / Watford every 15 minutes and between Baker Street and Harrow-on-the-Hill every 15 minutes. 
